               <p>RICHARD GEORGE SPICE. I am a <rs id="t18280911-301-viclabel1547" type="occupation">ham dealer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-301-victim1661 t18280911-301-viclabel1547"></join>. On the 21st of July I saw the prisoner take part of a ham from my shop - I gave an alarm, and he dropped it on the step of the door; he went out at one door and I at another and took him; he had run along the window, which is about a yard and a half.</p>


               <p>Prisoner. Q. Did you not swear you could not positively say it was me? A. No I did not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-301-person1662">
