            . I was sent for, and took the prisoner in charge - and in going along he feigned intoxication, and said it was a lark.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I said I thought they were having a lark - I came from my work and it began to rain; I was them going past the shop, the gentleman came out and took me.</p>
